State of Permutation(माथापच्ची)
==============================================
This is the state of mind when it realize there are more than one phase of process at certain 
instance of situation.In this state mind are in confused state it realize one 
phase of process is better/secure/happiest/right
/strong..etc than other phase of process.In this state mind live(streaming) all the 
information collected in past and after analysis of that information mind break
the solution of the situation in many part and try to select one part since that part look better than others.

***Neither any process is better than other process nor worse than other process***

If one observe, one can get during process of permutation lot of energy mind get release and due to 
release of energy state of mind come down lower state,
in lower state where permutation take lead for process of mind.
At this state mind not process the permutation but the permutation make/force mind to process
since the situation really look like serious.

***Fighting with self created jungle/network never realize a glance of mingle with self***
***Neither situation is tight nor it is light...looking any thing as situation it become situation***

